Package net.marfgamer.raknet

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Packet
    Used to read and write data with ease
    RakNet
    Contains info for RakNet
    RakNetClientTest
    Used to test RakNetClient by connecting to the Lifeboat Survival Games server and then disconnecting afterwards
    RakNetPacket
    A generic RakNet packet that has the ability to get the ID of the packet along with encoding and decoding
    RakNetServerTest
    Used to test RakNetServer by starting a server on the default
    SplitPacketTest
    Used to test the split packet feature of RakNetSession through a stress test by sending a packet as big as possible (Average packet size is over 146,000 bytes!)
    UtilityTest
    Used to test the various functions in RakNetUtils
